\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare.
\ip \fig [introduction - needs no cap]|src="HK-19D.tif" size="span" loc="1/4 page picture spans both columns" copy="Horace Knowles/Louise Bass" ref="Rom 1:0"\fig* Por khueŇč nzuav ana kha gava khergiap, RomiŇč ndi mbarigi. Ana Rom Ňčgu bak…®men guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n panan ruagi gumgi gu mbigi gan…®ngeŇč vuzvugiap, mba gava khergiap, mbe ndi mbarigi. Ana khueŇč vuzvugi, ana Ňčg…®p, tuga t…®vaneŇčra mbe phorg…® keg…®p, mbe thav Ňčg…®p, Spenan Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun suanga. Por mba gava kherav, ana guigira Krais buni vhuuiŇč, ana guigira nta siga sarav, nta bun mbe nzuav, vh…®ra ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi k…®rga k…®r…®r t…®vi mbun mbe nzuai. Por mba gava kherav, ana fharav won raar vhuun mba guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi mbe Roman ki, ana raar vhuun mbe nd…®…®v khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúGu zazera nden kurkura zav nde nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai.‚ÄĚ Ana maaŇč mbe suaŇčgiap, ana zumgum mba gava khergiap, mbe ndi mbai, ne n…®…®eŇč bun mbe nzuai. Ana khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúNza guigira Zisas khoth…®gi, mba tuavra, nza Fhe Bak…®me n…®man nza t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi ki.‚ÄĚ 1.17 Por khaŇč mbe nzuai, ‚ÄúKha gumgi gu mbigi zam, mbe ZudaiŇč o, mbe harigi fhaiŇč nt…®…®ri, mbe za t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi gu mbigi ma.‚ÄĚ
\ip MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me mbe korar muuŇčgip, ana taagip mbe ndigirga. Guma guigira Zisas Krais khoth…®g…®rga, Fhe Bak…®me taagip mba guma ndigirga. Mba guma, ana Fhe Bak…®men k…®vntok k…®v, ana Zisas Krais phorga r…®gi gumgi k…®rga. Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč muuŇčgip guma the ndigirga, mba guma, ana t…®var kama ndigap, ana ana z…®n vui.
\ip Ana fhum z…®n vugi t…®va vur, ana ana thagi. Ana t…®var kama z…®n vui. Mba guma Fhe Bak…®me ana phorga kim, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäinan Ňäaar guigira ana phorga ki. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, t…®vi mbat…®gi gu za rimgiap za vh…®zi ŇčkasŇčka, ana mbevav, ana gangirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Kha gavar Sapta 5 kegap gara vov Sapta 8 th…®gi. Por Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi n…®…®Ňčge bun nzuav, vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar guigira Zisas Krais khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigir ndavi vherir Ňčgari ŇčkasŇčka bun nzuai. Kha gavar Sapta 9 kega vov Sapta 11 th…®gi. Por ana simt…®ga bak…®me bun nzuai. Por vh…®ra ana Zuda guma ma.
\ip Mbe ZudaiŇč, mbe fhum Fhe Bak…®me mben wora mbuigi, mbe ana gumgi gu mbigi ma. Mbe ZudaiŇč, mbe ntigem, mben gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve mbe k…®r Zisas ga segi. Mbe harigi fhain Ňčguir ki gumgi gu mbigi vh…®rve, mbe ntigem, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi ki. Mbe ZudaiŇč, mbe fhu. Por ne nzuav khaŇč nzuai, mbe ZudaiŇč, mbe nduarira pham muuŇčgi. Mbe mba Fhe Bak…®me mben muun zav mbui big…®na bak…®me, mbe ne gangiap ne kaŇčgi fhuvara. Por kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, mbe ZudaiŇč, mbe zumgum, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui gumgi gu mbigi vhen zir…®rga. Por kha gava kherav mba bunin mbe nzua vov, mpuur ana Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n panan ruagi gumgi gu mbigi z…®n Ňčg…®rga t…®va bun mbe nzuai. Ana guigira k…®vgiap kha t…®var muun zav mbe nzuai, mba t…®v khare. Mbe guigira harigi gumgi gu mbigi vuzvug…®p, t…®vir vhuuiŇčra mben muun za nzuai. Ana vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®men Ňčaarar muuŇčv, Ňčgui gari guman pana piin k…®v, vh…®ra harigi gumgir kurkurarga nen mbe nzuai.
\c 1
\ms1 Nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, mba tuavra, nza Fhe Bak…®me n…®man nza t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi ki.
\s1 Por, Zisas wo Ňčaarar muun zav ana farasarigim, ana wo mbua ruigi Ňčaari neŇčgi buni khare.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt FG 9.15; 13.2; 22.21; 1 Ko 1.1; Ga 1.15\x*Gu, Por, gu Krais Zisasan Ňčaara guma. Ana nan kamgiap, na farasarigim, gu ana Ňčaara guma ma. Ana won Ňčaarar muun zav na farasarigi, gu Fhe Bak…®men buna vhuueŇč bun suanga.
\p 
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt FG 26.6; Ro 3.21; 16.25-26; Ga 3.8; Ta 1.2\x*Fhum Fhe Bak…®me kha buna vhuueŇč suaŇčgi, ana kamthooŇč gumgi ana buneŇč khergim, mba buneŇč ana gavar Ňčaarar ki.
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Mt 22.42; Ru 1.32; Zo 1.14; FG 2.30; Ro 9.5; Ga 4.4; 2 T 2.8\x*Mba buni, anan Kama bun nzuai bunin vhuuiŇč ma. Anan Kam, ana guma guara gegi. Ana kha nuianan Ňčgui vh…®rve gari guman pan Devit sh…®gar mbiga mbe ana tegim, ana anan nz…®k ki.
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt FG 13.33; Hi 9.14\x*Ana Fhe Bak…®me han kegap, zergap, ana Fhe Bak…®mera fara muuŇčgiap Ňčgarigi. Fhe Bak…®me, ana won ŇčkasŇčka bak…®men nza kh…®vav, ana rimgim, ana taagia ana khavgi. Ana maaŇč muuŇčgim, Fhe Bak…®me khuen nza kh…®vigi, ana anan Kam ma. Ana Zisas Krais, ana nza Bak…®me ma.
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt FG 26.16-18; Ro 12.3; 15.18; 1 Ko 15.10; Ga 2.7-9; Ef 3.8\x*Zisas Krais Ňčaarar panan Fhe Bak…®me fhura nzan kora muuŇčgiap, ana z…® k…®v…®r zav Fhe Bak…®me won buna vhuueŇč bun suanga Ňčaarar muun zav nzan farasegi. Ana mba t…®var muuŇčgirim, mba harigi fhaiŇč Ňčguir ki nt…®…®rir kam…®nga, mbe zam Zisas Krais khoth…®g…®p, ana z…®n Ňčg…®rga.
\v 6 Nde RomiŇč, nde vh…®ra Zisas nt…®…®ri ma. Fhe Bak…®me vh…®ra nden kamgim, nde Zisas Krais nt…®…®ri ki.
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Nam 6.25-26; 1 Ko 1.2-3; 2 Ko 1.1; Ga 1.3; Ef 1.2; 1 Te 4.7\x*Nde Roman guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, Fhe Bak…®me won ndavar nde n…®…®Ňčgiap, nden kamgim, nde anan gumgi gu mbigi kim, gu kha gava khergiap mba bunin za nde ndi mbai. Nzan Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum nzan Bak…®me Zisas Krais, mani fhura nden korar muuŇčv, nden ndavir muuŇčgirim, nde ndavi mb…®rav k…®ri.
\s1 Por RomiŇč gan…®ngane vuzvugi.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Fi 1.3; Kor 1.3-4; 1 Te 1.2; 1.8\x*Gu fharav khaŇč nde suan za mbui. Gu khueŇč mbararagi, kha nuianan za kha Ňčguir, kha gumgi nde Zisas khoth…®gi t…®va sh…®mandi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu za nde nd…®knd…®gap, gu Zisas Krais z…®n panan, gu wo Fhe Bak…®men ndikndigap ana phorga nzuai.
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt FG 19.21; Ro 15.23; 15.32; 2 Ko 1.23; Ef 1.16; Fi 1.8; 1 Te 2.5; 2.10; 3.10; 2 T 1.3; Ze 4.15\x*Gu guigira wo ndavar Fhe Bak…®me n…®…®Ňčgiap, anan Ňčaara mbuav, ana Kaman buna vhuueŇč bun nzuai. Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgi, gu zazera nde nd…®knd…®gap nde nzuav ana phorga nzuai.
\v 10 Gu zazera Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, gu zazera khaŇč ana nzuai. Ana vuzvuk ma, ana vuzvugirga, ana na ndi tuavar muuŇčgirga, gu nde han mbar Ňčg…®rga.
\v 11 Gu guigira nde gan…®ngeŇč vuzvugi. Gu khueŇč nzuav, gu Ňčg…®p, nde gan…®p, Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar na farve panan won Ňčaarar muun saŇčv fhura nde nd…®…®i ŇčkasŇčka, ana anan nden n…®…®nga, ana nden kurarim, nde havhargirga.
\v 12 Na nd…®knd…®k khaŇč muuŇčgia ki. Gu vuzvugi, nde Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, ana nan kurkurarga, gu vh…®ra Zisas khoth…®gi t…®v, ana vh…®ra nden kurarga. Mba t…®v za nza ndavi havhargirga.
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt Zo 15.15-16; FG 19.21; Ro 15.23; 16.7; Fi 4.17\x*Nde na phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, gu vuzvugi, nde tuituigip khueŇč kaŇčgiri. Gu tugi vh…®rvera nden han Ňčg…®r zav nd…®knd…®gi. Gu mbui Ňčaar ana harigi fhaiŇč Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigir kurkurigim, mbe guigira Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui. Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap, vh…®ra nden kurkurargane vuzvugi. Gu maaŇč muun za mbuim, bigi zazera na tuav gora zav ntige kha tugen h…®gi.
\v 14 Fhe Bak…®me Grikin kurkura zav Ňčaarar na nd…®…®v, ana vh…®ra harigi nt…®…®rir kurkura zav Ňčaarar na nd…®…®v, ana vh…®ra mba nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki gumgi gum nd…®knd…®k vhuuiŇč ki fhuv gumgir kurkura zav Ňčaarar na n…®…®Ňčgi. Gu mba Ňčaarara muunga.
\v 15 MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun nde RomiŇč gumgi gu mbigi, gu nta bun nde suan zav nan ndav guigira khavgi.
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč, ne Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčka ma.
\p 
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Sng 119.46; Mk 8.38; FG 3.26; 13.46; 1 Ko 1.18-24; 2 T 1.8\x*Gu Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun suangen mberi fhu. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®men ŇčkasŇčka, ana buna vhuuen ki. Mba ŇčkasŇčka, ana guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, ana taagia mbe ndi. Mba ŇčkasŇčka, ana fhara ZudaiŇč ndigip, ana vh…®ra harigi fhaiŇč nt…®…®ri ndig…®rga.
\v 17 \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Hab 2.4; Zo 3.36; Ro 3.21-22; Ga 3.11; Hi 10.38\x*Mba Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇčra Fhe Bak…®me won t…®var vhuun nza mbuav, t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigir nzan kaai tuav k…®rar h…®gi. Nza Fhe Bak…®me khoth…®g…®rga, ana kha z…®n nzan kam…®nga, nza t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi ma. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nza guigira Zisas khoth…®gim, Fhe Bak…®me t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigir nzan kaai. Ne nza ana khoth…®gi tuavra kega vov, mba tuavra vh…®zgi. Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap nera nzuai, ‚ÄúGuigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, Fhe Bak…®me kha z…®n mben kaai, mbe t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui gumgi gu mbigi ma. Mbe nzerara k…®rga.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Gumgi gu mbigi za k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segi.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 1:18 \xt FG 17.30; Ef 5.6; Kor 3.6; 2 Te 2.12\x*Nza kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me Hevenan kav, ana guigira won ndav shir…® ndiv k…®ra kh…®ngi. Ana mba k…®r ana segap t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi, ana mbe mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana guigira vhega mbat…®gar ntan muuŇčgirga. Mbe mba t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, mbe Fhe Bak…®me bun nzuai buni guari, mbe nta mbevigi.
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Zo 1.9; FG 14.15-17; 17.24-28\x*Mba gumgi, mbe Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi vh…®rve, mbe nta kaŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me nduara mba t…®vir mbe kh…®vigi. Mbe nta thav, k…®r ana segim, ana mba t…®va mbat…®gar mbe mbui.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Jop 12.7-9; Sng 19.1; FG 14.17; 17.27; Hi 11.3\x*Fhum Fhe Bak…®me fhara guarara za kha bigi ga muuŇčgi tugen kegap, zav ntige kha tuge th…®gi. Kha gumgi, mbe za ana muuŇčgi bigi gangi. Mbe mba tuavar, mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip kaŇčgirga, Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi mbari zorga khar ki. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgip Fhe Bak…®men t…®vi n…®…®Ňčge kaŇčgip, mbe vh…®ra ana ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me ana zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki, mbe vh…®ra ana kaŇčgirga. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, guma the guigira khaŇč suanga fhu, ‚ÄúGu kaŇčgi fhu. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, gu thaneŇč Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgi fhu.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Jer 2.5; Ef 4.17-18\x*Mbe Fhe Bak…®me kaŇčgi, mbe ana z…® ndiv vun kuamkuagi fhu. Mbe vh…®ra ana ndikndigi bunin ana nzuai fhu. Mbe maaŇč muuŇčgiap mben nd…®knd…®gi ŇčanŇčangiap g…®ng…®ngi, mbe fhura g…®ng…®nan ki.
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Jer 10.14; 1 Ko 1.20\x*Mbe kav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNza nd…®knd…®gi vhuuiŇč ki.‚ÄĚ Fhuvara. Mbe guigira ŇčanŇčangi.
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Lo 4.16-18; Sng 106.20; Jer 2.11; Ese 8.10; FG 17.29\x*Mbe zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki Fhe Bak…®me, ana guigira ŇčkasŇčka ki, mbe k…®r ana segap, ana rotu mbui fhu. Mbe vh…®zi gumgi ntuu karav, mbe korgi ntuu karav, s…®gi ntuu karav, kurugi ntuu karav, mbaari ntuu karav, ntan rotu mbui.
\s1 Mba gumgi gu mbigi mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe nta mbui.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt FG 7.42; 14.16; 1 Ko 6.18; Ef 4.18; 1 Te 4.4\x*Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segim, Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč muuŇčgiap mbe thagi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me mbe thagim, mben nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gi mbe Ňčg…®rgim, mbe t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbuav wari t…®gap t…®vi mbat…®gir nduarira wari wo fhavi ndirara mbui.
\v 25 \x - \xo 1:25 \xt Ais 44.20; Jer 13.25; 16.19; Amo 2.4; Ro 9.5; 1 Te 1.9; 1 Zo 5.20\x*Mba khesharigi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe Fhe Bak…®men buni guari, mbe nta thav, fhura guiguigi buni, mbe nta ndigi. Mbe nta ndigap, za kha bigi ga muuŇčgi Fhe Bak…®me, mbe k…®r ana segap, mbe ana muuŇčgi bigi, mbe nta rotu mbuav, nta piin ki. Fhe Bak…®me, ana za kha bigi n…®…®Ňčge ma. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nza zazera ana z…® ndiv vun kuamkuarga. Ne guigira.
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 1:26 \xt Wkp 18.22-23; Ef 5.12\x*Mbe maaŇč mbuav k…®r Fhe Bak…®me segim, Fhe Bak…®me mbe thagim, mbe won ndavir vuri vuzvugi t…®vi, mbe nta z…®n vov, guigira mberi t…®vi mbat…®gir warira mbui. Mbe kav, mben mbigi vh…®ra, mbe mani gu mburi wari ga r…®gi t…®vi guari, mbe nta thav, guigira mberi t…®vi mbat…®gir warira mbui.
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27 \xt Wkp 18.22; 20.13; 1 Ko 6.9\x*Mben gumgi vh…®ra, mbe mani gu mburi wari ga r…®gi t…®vi guari thav, mben ndavi vhava fara muuŇčgiap khavav, mbe mberi t…®vi mbat…®gir warira mbui. Mbe mber…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gir taagia warira mbui. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mbe nduarira mba mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi Ňčgarkav, mba vheza mbat…®ga ndigi.
\v 28 Mbe Fhe Bak…®me piin k…®v ana nd…®knd…®g…®rgeŇč thagi. MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me fhura mbe garav, mbe thagim, mbe nd…®knd…®gi guigira mbat…®gim, mbe nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gi z…®n Ňčg…®rga. Mbe nta z…®n vov, mbe guma muunga fhuv t…®vi mbat…®gi guarira mbe nta mbui.
\v 29 Mbe mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi guigira mbe givigi. Mbe t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbuav, mbe harigi gumgi bigi garav, niih…® mbat…®gar nta mbuav, t…®vi mbat…®gi warira mbui. Mbe vh…®ra bigi vh…®rve ki gumgi, mbe mbe nzuav ndavi shiav, mbe harigi gumgi shogim, mbe vh…®zim, mbe fhura tamtam ntari ga mbuav, fhura guiguigap, mbe vh…®ra nd…®knd…®gi mbat…®gir harigi gumgi ga mbui. Mbe vh…®ra harigi gumgi z…®n mbaav mbe nzuai.
\v 30 Mbe vh…®ra harigi gumgir z…®rir farfav, mbe sh…®sh…®gi bunin mbe nzuai. Mbe vh…®ra panara thav Fhe Bak…®me garav, fhura tuava purav, ndikndigap surav, harigi gumgi mbevav, kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, ‚ÄúNza fegi ma.‚ÄĚ Mbe vh…®ra wari wo z…®ri ndi vun kuamkuagi. Mbe maaŇč mbuav, mbe vh…®ra t…®vi mbat…®gir Ňčkaa, mbe nta ndiav nta mbui. Mbe maaŇč mbuav wari won ndegi gu ndegmbori nzuai buni, mbe nta daasui.
\v 31 Mbe nd…®knd…®gi kav bigi ga mbui fhu. Mbe wari wo nzuai buni mbararav, mbe nduarira wari wo nzuai buni, mbe guigira nta z…®n vui fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra wari wo phorge regi v…®z…®na bavira, vuzvugap t…®vir vhuuin wari ga mbui fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra harigi gumgi gu mbigi kora mbui fhuvara.
\v 32 \x - \xo 1:32 \xt Sng 50.18; Hos 7.3; Ro 2.2; 6.21\x*Fhe Bak…®men t…®var vhuuŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúMba khesharigi t…®vi ga mbui gumgi, mbe vh…®z…®rga.‚ÄĚ Mba gumgi, mbe mba t…®v, mbe tuituigiap ana kaŇčgi. Mbe ana kaŇčgiap, mbe ana daasuav, mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi, mbe nta mbuavra ki. Mbe vh…®ra mba t…®vi mbat…®gira mbui fhuvara. Mbe vh…®ra mba khesharigi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi, mbe vh…®ra mbe z…®ri ndi vun kuamkuagi.
\c 2
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav suanga buni, nta th…®g…®ra mbarav Ňčg…®g…®rga.
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Mt 7.1; Ru 6.37; Zo 8.7-9; Ro 1.20\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde gumgi zam, nde fhura bunin harigi gumgi ga sav mbe nzuai. Gu za nde fh…®gira ph…®rav nde nzuai, nde the khaŇč suaŇč thari, ‚ÄúGu t…®va mbat…®ga thueŇč muuŇčgi fhuvara.‚ÄĚ Nde mbarara. Nde maaŇč mbuav, bunin harigi gumgi ga sav, nde vh…®ra mba bunin warira si. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nde vh…®ra mba khesharigi t…®vara mbui nt…®…®ri ma.
\v 2 Nza kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me mba khesharigi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi, ana vheza mbat…®gar mbe nd…®…®i. Fhe Bak…®me mba t…®va mbui, ne guigira nzerigi.
\v 3 Nde vh…®ra gumgi gu mbigira, nde mba khesharigi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi gu mbigi, nde farar mbe sav mbe nzuai. Nde vh…®ra mbe mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi, nde vh…®ra nta mbui. Nde khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi thi? Fhe Bak…®me nde suaŇčv suaŇčgirga fhuv thi?
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Ais 30.18; Ro 3.25; Ef 1.7; 2.9; 2 Pi 3.9; 3.15\x*Nde ram muuŇčgi nt…®…®ri? Fhe Bak…®me t…®var vhuun nde mbuav, nde rarga tuga mpeeŇčra kav, ana vhemkora nde mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi ga nzuav, vhemkora vhezar nde nd…®…®i fhuvara. Fhe Bak…®me mba t…®var vhuun nde mbuim, nde mba t…®va garim, ana fhura mba t…®var nde mbui thi? Fhe Bak…®me khueŇč vuzvugi, nde ndavi domdor…®ri. Ana ne nzuav mba t…®var vhuun nde mbui. Ee, nde ne kaŇčgi fhuv thi?
\v 5 Nde guigira wari won ndavi p…®ngiap, ndavi domdor…® thagi. Nde mba t…®va mbuav, nde nduarira ne nzuav vheza bak…®men warira t…® suav ndai. Fhe Bak…®me za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi ga suaŇčv suanga tugar, ana guigira ndav shir…® k…®rar h…®rga, nde ne suaŇčv vheza mbat…®ga ndirga.
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Sng 62.12; Snd 24.12; Mt 16.27; Zo 5.29; 1 Ko 3.8; 2 Ko 5.10; VB 22.12\x*Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč ki gap khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúFhe Bak…®me mba gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi tug…®ra t…®g…®p vhezar mben n…®…®nga.‚ÄĚ
\v 7 Gumgi mbari, mbe khaŇč t…®gap ŇčkasŇčkagiap t…®vi vhuuiŇč z…®n vov, mbe Fhe Bak…®me han Hevenan tuituigip perav, z…® bak…®me ndiv, zazera mbara muuŇčgiap kav vh…®zi fhuv b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňč ndirga tuavi ndi gari. Fhe Bak…®me zazera mbara muuŇčgiap ki b…®…®Ňčb…®…®n mba gumgi gu mbigir n…®…®nga.
