\v 10 Fhe Bak…®me Hevenan z…® bak…®me gum mpirmpir…®ga vhuun gum ndav m…®…®t…®gar t…®vir vhuuiŇč ga mbui gumgi gu mbigir n…®…®nga. Ana fharav Zudain n…®…®Ňčgip, ana vh…®ra mba harigi fhaiŇč Ňčgui gumgi gu mbigir n…®…®nga.
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Lo 10.17; 2 Sto 19.7; Jop 34.19; FG 10.34; Ga 2.6; Ef 6.9; Kor 3.25; 1 Pi 1.17\x*Fhe Bak…®me gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuav nzuai, ana za mba suambarara za mba gumgi gu mbigi ga mbui. Ana khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi fhuvara, mbe harigi nt…®…®ri ma. Ana mba nd…®knd…®ga mbui fhuvara.
