\v 24 \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Ais 52.5; Ese 36.20-23\x*Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč ki gap, ana mba t…®va nzuai kameŇč khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúNde pham mbuim, harigi fhain Ňčgui gumgi, mbe Fhe Bak…®me nz…®…®v buni mbat…®gi ana nzuai.‚ÄĚ
