\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Sng 5.9; 140.3; Ze 5.16\x*Mben kaathoori gumgi ndi mbogi ga r…®gi mbogi fara muuŇčgiap fhoms…®giap gumgi khurav nd…®ga hi fara muuŇčgi buni gum gumgi shogim, mbe vh…®zi buni ntan kav hi.
