\v 19 \x - \xo 3:19 \xt Zo 10.34; Ro 1.20; 2.2; 3.9; 3.23\x*Nza khueŇč kaŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me Moses ga n…®…®Ňčgi t…®vi, nta suaŇčgi t…®vi piin ki nt…®…®ri, nta mben t…®vi ma. Fhe Bak…®me Moses ga n…®…®Ňčgi t…®vi khueŇč nzuai ne khaŇč muuŇčgi. Nza kha gumgi, nza zam, nzan guma the Fhe Bak…®me Ňčgarkarga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Nza kha nuianan ki gumgi, nza zam Fhe Bak…®me n…®ma thivgirim, ana nza suaŇčv suaŇčgirga.
\v 20 \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Sng 143.2; FG 13.39; Ro 7.7; Ga 2.16; Ef 2.8-9; Ta 3.5\x*Guma the Fhe Bak…®me Moses ga n…®…®Ňčgi t…®vi z…®n vui ne suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui guman anan kamgirga tukt…®gi fhuvara. Fhe Bak…®me Moses ga n…®…®Ňčgi t…®vi, nta nza mbui t…®vi mbat…®gir nza kh…®vi.
\s1 Guma guigira Krais khoth…®gi, ana kha z…® ki, t…®vir vhuuiaŇč mbui guma.
